s</i> ‘lord’ + ‘great’, but if so, it is not clear that it survives today."]}]},{"name":"Fru","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Transferred use of the surname, in origin denoting either a free person rather than a serf (from Old English <i>frīg</i> ‘free’, a byform of <i>frēo</i>) or else a small person (from Old Norse <i>frió</i> ‘seed’).  Elizabeth Fry  (  1780–1845 ) was a celebrated Quaker prison reformer."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Fru Ivarsson was born in 1400, in Åland, Finland. She had at least 1 son with Ivar Nilsson. She died in 1480, in her hometown, at the age of 80."},"et":{"1400–1480":"1400–1480","1400–1475":"1400–1475","1420–1472":"1420–1472","1400":"1400","1420":"1420","1475":"1475","1472":"1472","after 1472":"pärast 1472","1480":"1480","Älvsborg, Sweden":"Älvsborg, Rootsi","Älvsborg, Norrbotten, Sweden":"Älvsborg, Norrbotten, Rootsi","Kastelholm, Åland, Finland":"Åland, Soome","Kastelholm, Aland, Finland":"Åland, Soome"},"fi":{"1400–1480":"1400–1480","1400–1475":"1400–1475","1420–1472":"1420–1472","1400":"1400","1420":"1420","1475":"1475","1472":"1472","after 1472":"1472 jälkeen","1480":"1480","Älvsborg, Sweden":"Älvsborg, Ruotsi","Älvsborg, Norrbotten, Sweden":"Älvsborg, Norrbotten, Ruotsi","Kastelholm, Åland, Finland":"Ahvenanmaa, Suomi","Kastelholm, Aland, Finland":"Ahvenanmaa, Suomi"},"fr":{"1400–1480":"1400–1480","1400–1475":"1400–1475","1420–1472":"1420–1472","1400":"1400","1420":"1420","1475":"1475","1472":"1472","after 1472":"après 1472","1480":"1480","Älvsborg, Sweden":"Älvsborg, Suède","Älvsborg, Norrbotten, Sweden":"Älvsborg, Norrbotten, Suède","Kastelholm, Åland, Finland":"Åland, Finlande","Kastelholm, Aland, Finland":"Åland, Finlande","lifeSummary":"Fru Ivarsson est née en 1400, à Åland, Finlande. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Ivar Nilsson. Elle est décédée en 1480, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 80 ans."},"de":{"1400–1480":"1400–1480","1400